long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Browser extension to test Dotmetrics analytics script for IPSOS multinational market research and consulting firm. Extension detects Dotmetrics script on pages that uses Dotmetrics analytics. Extension displays useful data from Dotmetrics script for testing purposes and debugging.
